text = "Controls
									Keyboard				Controller
	Movement:			WASD / arrow keys		leftstick
	Interact:				   F / space					 B / X
	Sprint (hold):		  	  shift						  A
	Restart game:				 R					 start button

Intro

	You are a Triage Nurse.
	Your job is to treat as many patients as you can
	during your shift time.
	Be aware,
	patients arrving won't last very long, save them!

How to Play

	Heal Patients:
		- Put patients on their corresponding bed

		- Apply corresponding medicine to the on-bed patients
		  to start healing them
			* When healing process starts,
			   patient’s will stop dying

	Extract Patients:
		- Pickup the healed patients and place them 
		  at the exit area to allow them to leave
	
	Aim:
		- Treat and extract as many patients as you can
		  during your shift
		- Don’t let them die

	* ICU bed can treat any patient type
	  without the need for medicine!"

